de.fub.agg2graph.agg

Interface ICachingStrategy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultCachingStrategy

    public interface ICachingStrategy
    Strategy for caching data. Includes methods for adding, removing, loading, and saving AggNodes and AggConnections. Also handles proximity searches and clipping AggNodes from a specified area.
    Author:
    Johannes Mitlmeier
